
Code for the paper `Tokens enable cooperation without identification or memory' by Marcus Frean and Stephen Marsland.

To generate royal roads, use
julia run-royal-roads.jl

and to test all strategies and social norms use
julia make_datas.jl

For both of these, parameter choices are in the file

To make the plots use
python plot_results.py (with command-line options, see the code)

Test functions should be self-explanatory
